All Profile Dim - Frame 72X35mm, Sash bottom19X39.5mm with (Min Height :400mm Max :1600 mm) and (Min: Width 700mm max: 2400 mm) with Toughened Glass upto 8 mm Thickness and 789 grade weather silicon.
